        <paragraph>Mesh optimized for creating geometry manually.</paragraph>
        <section classes="classref-introduction-group" ids="description" names="description">
            <title>Description</title>
            <paragraph>A mesh type optimized for creating geometry manually, similar to OpenGL 1.x immediate mode.</paragraph>
            <paragraph>Here's a sample on how to generate a triangular face:</paragraph>
